desc_short	-----								The South Seas are calling! Summer, sun, beach, and palm trees. Who doesn't pine for a life in the southern clime? This dream is now coming true. Transform a pristine beach into a popular travel destination by using strategic skill and economical thinking. Give free rein to your creativity!							
